                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240218-159-off871 t18240218-159-cd872"></join>, a cheese, value 6 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240218-159-victim1486" type="victimName">
                     Joshua 
